name: Vimeo
body:
### Welcome to Java Vimeo API 3.0.
To use this api you’ll first need to register your app from here:

https://developer.vimeo.com/apps

In your app you need to generate an Access Token with upload access.
The generated Token is all you need to use this API.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Contact info@clickntap.com and we’ll help you sort it out.
